{"id":66,"date":"2015-01-10T10:39:25","date_gmt":"2015-01-10T10:39:25","guid":{"rendered":"http:\/\/berrytree.org\/?page_id=66"},"modified":"2025-07-28T15:06:25","modified_gmt":"2025-07-28T19:06:25","slug":"home","status":"publish","type":"page","link":"https:\/\/berrytree.org\/","title":{"rendered":"Berrytree Home"},"content":{"rendered":"\n<p>Welcome to Berrytree.org. Home of the genealogical data collected and curated by Benjamin Henderson and his sons Berry and Aaron on Robert Berry (Princess Ann County Va.) b.~1729.  We strive to provide to keep only the most accurate and up to date information on Robert Berry and his descendants.  Please join us on Facebook and Wikitree.org to help keep this site home of the best information available for this family. If you have any questions about joining the Facebook group or getting involved with Wikitree, please use the <a href=\"https:\/\/berrytree.org\/contact-us\/\">contact us<\/a> link and we&#8217;ll help you with joining the Berrytree online Community.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<h3 class=\"wp-block-heading has-text-align-center\"><a href=\"https:\/\/berrytree.org\/benjamin-berry-henderson-sr\/\">In memory of Benjamin &#8220;Ben&#8221; Henderson 1930-2020<\/a><\/h3>\n\n\n\n<h1 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Site Navigation Aids<\/h1>\n\n\n\n<p><strong><a href=\"https:\/\/berrytree.org\/page-updates\/\">Page Updates<\/a>:<\/strong> Pages ordered by when they were updated<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p><strong>Search Berrytree Website:<\/strong> &#8221;&nbsp;in the <em>Search Box<\/em> or the <em>Side Bar<\/em>&nbsp;&#8221;&nbsp;&nbsp;<img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"60\" height=\"21\" class=\"wp-image-8101\" style=\"width: 60px;\" src=\"http:\/\/berrytree.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2015\/01\/barpointer32-e1556549631259.png\" alt=\"\"><\/p>\n\n\n\n<p><strong><a href=\"https:\/\/berrytree.org\/name-index\/\">Alphabetical&nbsp;Name Index<\/a>:<\/strong>&nbsp; Lists names ordered by last name<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p><strong><a href=\"https:\/\/berrytree.org\/by-family-line\/\">By Family Line<\/a>:<\/strong> List family pages ordered by generation<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p><strong><a href=\"https:\/\/berrytree.org\/alphabetical-pages-index\/\">Alphabetical Pages Index<\/a>:&nbsp;<\/strong>Lists names ordered by first name<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>Also, if you cannot find what you are searching for and believe it should be include on this site, please use the <a href=\"https:\/\/berrytree.org\/contact-us\/\">Contact Us<\/a> link to email us and we will be glad to help you.<\/p>\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-image\">\n<figure class=\"aligncenter is-resized\"><a href=\"https:\/\/berrytree.org\/dnapagetwo\/\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"493\" height=\"99\" src=\"http:\/\/berrytree.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2015\/01\/YDNA-3.png\" alt=\"YDNA 3\" class=\"wp-image-8126\" style=\"width:269px;height:54px\" srcset=\"https:\/\/berrytree.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2015\/01\/YDNA-3.png 493w, https:\/\/berrytree.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2015\/01\/YDNA-3-300x60.png 300w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 493px) 100vw, 493px\" \/><\/a><\/figure><\/div>\n\n\n<p><\/p>\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-image\">\n<figure class=\"aligncenter\"><a href=\"https:\/\/berrytree.org\/robertberrypac\/\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"200\" height=\"44\" src=\"http:\/\/berrytree.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2015\/01\/NUMBER-ONE-GEN-A-e1556578111518.png\" alt=\"NUMBER ONE GEN A\" class=\"wp-image-8114\"\/><\/a><\/figure><\/div>\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-image\">\n<figure class=\"alignleft\"><a href=\"https:\/\/berrytree.org\/robert-berry-oc\/\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"200\" height=\"46\" src=\"http:\/\/berrytree.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2015\/01\/NUMBER-TWO-GEN-B-e1556578367426.png\" alt=\"NUMBER TWO GEN B\" class=\"wp-image-8116\"\/><\/a><\/figure><\/div>\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-image\">\n<figure class=\"alignright\"><a href=\"https:\/\/berrytree.org\/genthree\/\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"200\